no depende del criterio geográfico; iii) tampoco queda restringido a las características exclusivas de la propia lengua; y iv) aparece en otras lenguas romances. Los fenómenos gramaticales analizados en este volumen son doce: adjetivos elativos, numerales cardinales, estructuras posesivas nominales, subida del clítico, concordancias ad sensum, concordancia en verbos seudoimpersonales, morfología flexiva inesperada, construcciones presentacionales, infinitivo por imperativo, estructuras seudocoordinadas, deísmo y estructuras sintácticas híbridas.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2022) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aArquiola, Elena Felíu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBosque, Ignacio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBouzouita, Miriam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDi Tullio, Ángela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFábregas, Antonio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGallego, Ángel J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKornfeld, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLópez, Cristina Sánchez, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMare, María, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoreno, Carlota de Benito, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPato, Enrique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPato, Enrique, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aResnik, Gabriela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSitaridou, Ioanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabul